Citation.sAbstract: Vapour liquid equilibria at atmospheric pressure for binary mixtures of n-heptane + bromobenzene, +chlorobenzene and +fluorobenzene have been determined. These have been shown to be thermodynamically consistent.
Citation.sTitle: Isobaric vapour liquid equilibria for binary mixtures of n-heptane with bromobenzene, chlorobenzene and fluorobenzene at atmospheric pressure
